name: Appartement
description:
Appartement is situated in Marrakech, 1.9 km from Mouassine Museum, 1.5 km from Koutoubia Mosque, and 1.8 km from Yves Saint Laurent Museum. The air-conditioned accommodation is 1.8 km from Majorelle Gardens, and guests can benefit from private parking available on site and free WiFi. The property is non-smoking and is located 1.8 km from Djemaa El Fna.

The spacious apartment features a balcony, 2 bedrooms, a living room and a well-equipped kitchen with a fridge and a minibar. A flat-screen TV is provided.

Marrakesh Train Station is 2.2 km from the apartment, while Le Jardin Secret is 1.7 km away. The nearest airport is Marrakech-Menara Airport, 4 km from Appartement.

name: Spacious 2BR Apt in Sunny Agadir
description:
Set in Agadir in the Souss-Massa-Draa region, Spacious 2BR Apt in Sunny Agadir features a balcony and garden views. This property offers access to a terrace and free private parking. The property is non-smoking and is situated 5.1 km from Amazighe Heritage Museum.

The apartment is fitted with 1 bedroom, a flat-screen TV and a fully equipped kitchen that provides guests with an oven, a microwave, a washing machine, a fridge and a stovetop. Towels and bed linen are featured in the apartment. For added privacy, the accommodation features a private entrance.

Marina Agadir is 6.7 km from the apartment, while Medina Polizzi is 7 km away. The nearest airport is Agadir–Al Massira Airport, 19 km from Spacious 2BR Apt in Sunny Agadir.

name: Dar mektoube
description:
Situated in Casablanca, 5 km from Anfa Place Living Resort and 10 km from Morocco Mall, Dar mektoube offers air conditioning. The property is around 1.1 km from Casa Port Railway Terminal, 1.5 km from Ancient Medina of Casablanca and 3.7 km from Casa Voyageurs Train Station. The property is 700 metres from the city centre and 3.9 km from Hassan II Mosq.

The apartment is composed of 1 bedroom, a fully equipped kitchen, and 1 bathroom. A flat-screen TV is available. The accommodation is non-smoking.

Popular points of interest near the apartment include Central Market of Casablanca, Arab League Park and Casablanca Cathedral. The nearest airport is Mohammed V International Airport, 28 km from Dar mektoube.
